  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our Next Game</h1><p></p><br><h1>GAMES BY THE CREATOR OF CATO</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With enchanting graphics and an immersive soundtrack, \"The Traveler's Path\" is a challenging and fun game that will test your puzzle skills. Help the hero reach their destination and blaze new trails along the way. With each level presenting a unique combination of paths and obstacles, players must use their creativity and skill to find the perfect solution. <br><br>Are you ready to embark on this journey of discovery and adventure? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 50 challenging levels with various themes and mechanics.<br></li><li> Intuitive and responsive controls for smooth gameplay.<br></li><li> Multiple solutions for each puzzle, encouraging creative thinking.<br></li><li> A gradual increase in difficulty, allowing players to progress at their own pace.<br></li><li> Unlockable achievements and rewards for completing challenges and reaching milestones.<br></li><li> Suitable for all ages, offering fun and challenging puzzles for everyone to enjoy.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Conquer the traveller's path in a world of puzzles!</strong>",
